{"tid":232978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林健鋒：倘政府硬闖取消MPF對沖 中小企寧炒人轉合約制","createTime":"2017-05-07T08:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T14:57:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aaf17d358ffc9e3b755aaa7492a1ff3391236b7","tid":232978,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170507/large/1494127571_18c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170507%2Flarge%2F1494127571_18c5.jpg&h=73fcf0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、經民聯副主席林健鋒今早出席電台節目時，提到取消強積金對沖，指了解到目前各方並無就強積金對沖方案達成共識，但商界不認同政府提議的方案，認為政府10年後抽身，會嚴重加重商界經營負擔，更指假如政府硬闖，已聽聞有中小企表示寧願在新例實行前解僱所有員工，改行聘請合約制員工。<br />\n<br />\n林健鋒表示，商界主流現時提出新方案，在保留對沖前提下，商界及政府各增加1%強積金供款，保留對沖，並建議政府為僱員購買失業及退休保險。他希望政府平衡各方意見，並真正「落水」處理額外開支，認為現時仍有時間討論，方案不必急於兩、三個月內拍板。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林健鋒期望候任特首林鄭月娥順利組班，認為除了政府以外，亦可以在政府內部提拔人才，相信只要將人才放在正確位置就能收效。他亦說，大灣區是香港未來發展契機，期望本港把握機會，在工商金融、高新科技等有更大發展。"},{"pid":"87385a404bdcfc68e6312dc02ea0e2c4e8aa1d84","tid":232978,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ari-sensei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fari-sensei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F043.jpg&h=c92bb629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0e49492ccfd91927a9be53c02bf5abc9b381aa6","tid":232978,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://ari-sensei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fari-sensei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F043.jpg&h=c92bb629&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n好似酒樓咁, 做滿4年半, 即炒再轉頭請返"},{"pid":"93cba7ed2754111ac4df2b104903c1921c85f730","tid":232978,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"同埋政府先係用最多合約制機構<br />\n<br />\n中小企轉晒合約係唔出奇"},{"pid":"4ffcf8cae52559f9b16984447e6f7ddbf79bd4a1","tid":232978,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"而家都係請完炒，炒完請架啦"},{"pid":"70ed628dc995d6dcbe1b7cd52cab7d4d6be3658e","tid":232978,"uid":78154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老味,取消強姦金啦,<br />\n取消左對沖,政府又可以話自己做左野<br />\n之後咩都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b127551954b9f6fd5917642903b61b1a585ebd76","tid":232978,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"競爭力咁弱，呢啲企業黎一輸淘汰吧啦"},{"pid":"12f99215dfd606c2a59762b7d3806a2fc2f05168","tid":232978,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老味,取消強姦金啦,<br />\n取消左對沖,政府又可以話自己做左野<br />\n之後咩都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱，還原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞番公積金好過"},{"pid":"799e4b824b9aab749eba44e002146a9c16f58f84","tid":232978,"uid":104941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"直接取消強積金啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aa8e98de4c23faa52414ab6ba7bae8c7546510","tid":232978,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"呢十年有幾多份工唔係合約制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba33536e5a4cd47a06f6b49b4b18e04b78f553a1","tid":232978,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"合約制咪合約制囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講撚到你地請人唔係合約制咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfa6982c14d3ff6b2394f9b8